{
  "texts": [
    "The impact of this large-scale coordination is evident in several statistics from recent studies:",
    "The sheer volume and reach of AI-coordinated content is staggering.",
    "By one estimate, toxic misinformation spread via coordinated networks reaches millions of users daily and has affected political processes in over 50 countries (Johnson et al., 2024).",
    "This global penetration suggests that no region is immune; wherever social media use is prevalent, so too is the potential for AI-boosted disinformation to interfere with public discourse.",
    "The prevalence of bots as part of internet traffic highlights the magnitude of the challenge."
  ]
}